So the fix is not Lambda code and not CG password anymore.

The fix is: make RDS Proxy use IAM auth when it connects to Aurora.

AWS docs call this end to end IAM authentication, where both client to proxy and proxy to database use IAM authentication. AWS says this requires changing the proxy default auth scheme to IAM_AUTH and giving the proxy role rds-db:connect permissions.

